+++++maps_sprayTypes.xml+++++
***Map with no maps_sprayTypes.xml***
Copy all lines

***Map with existing maps_sprayTypes.xml***
copy <sprayTypes> to </sprayTypes> and paste in within the <maps> section



+++++maps_fillTypes.xml+++++
***Map has NO maps_fillTypes.xml***
Copy ALL lines of this file if your map currently has NO maps_fillTypes.xml file.

***Map has existing maps_fillTypes.xml***
Copy the from <fillType> to </fillType> for each respective fill type you are adding, and paste into the existing map XML file.  
Then add in the filltype name to the <fillTypeCategories> and <fillTypeSounds> sections as appropriate
